Comment: 0,0:22:10.29,0:22:14.68,ED - JP,,0,0,0,karaoke,面と向かって嘘をついても
Comment: 0,0:22:14.68,0:22:19.37,ED - JP,,0,0,0,karaoke,I can see through you
Comment: 0,0:22:21.25,0:22:25.73,ED - JP,,0,0,0,karaoke,あなたの影に隠れていても
Comment: 0,0:22:25.73,0:22:27.64,ED - JP,,0,0,0,karaoke,I'm tougher than you think
Comment: 0,0:22:27.64,0:22:30.16,ED - JP,,0,0,0,karaoke,Trust me, Trust me
Comment: 0,0:22:30.83,0:22:33.33,ED - JP,,0,0,0,karaoke,You keep coming back
Comment: 0,0:22:33.59,0:22:36.17,ED - JP,,0,0,0,karaoke,What keeps you grounded
Comment: 0,0:22:37.00,0:22:40.89,ED - JP,,0,0,0,karaoke,like gravity?
Comment: 0,0:22:41.83,0:22:46.95,ED - JP,,0,0,0,karaoke,帰る場所が別々でも
Comment: 0,0:22:47.84,0:22:51.64,ED - JP,,0,0,0,karaoke,抗えないYou and I
Comment: 0,0:22:51.92,0:22:54.85,ED - JP,,0,0,0,karaoke,落ちてくlike gravity
Comment: 0,0:22:55.36,0:23:00.23,ED - JP,,0,0,0,karaoke,彼の地を夢見て方舟は彷徨えど
Comment: 0,0:23:00.68,0:23:05.37,ED - JP,,0,0,0,karaoke,寄り添ってこう見上げてこう空let's keep it going
Comment: 0,0:23:06.30,0:23:11.37,ED - JP,,0,0,0,karaoke,あなたの心はあなただけのものでも
Comment: 0,0:23:11.76,0:23:13.16,ED - JP,,0,0,0,karaoke,Just so you know that
Comment: 0,0:23:13.16,0:23:17.20,ED - JP,,0,0,0,karaoke,there is always room for you in my heart
Comment: 0,0:23:17.54,0:23:20.61,ED - JP,,0,0,0,karaoke,What keeps you grounded
Comment: 0,0:23:20.88,0:23:23.96,ED - JP,,0,0,0,karaoke,like gravity
Comment: 0,0:23:25.71,0:23:30.96,ED - JP,,0,0,0,karaoke,帰る場所が別々でも
Comment: 0,0:23:31.87,0:23:35.40,ED - JP,,0,0,0,karaoke,抗えない絆
Comment: 0,0:23:35.71,0:23:38.71,ED - JP,,0,0,0,karaoke,Falling for you like gravity
Comment: 0,0:22:10.29,0:22:14.68,ED - CN,,0,0,0,karaoke,纵使你当面编织谎言
Comment: 0,0:22:14.68,0:22:19.37,ED - CN,,0,0,0,karaoke,我也能看透你的内心
Comment: 0,0:22:21.25,0:22:25.73,ED - CN,,0,0,0,karaoke,纵使你藏匿于自己的阴影中
Comment: 0,0:22:25.73,0:22:27.64,ED - CN,,0,0,0,karaoke,我的坚韧也超乎你想象
Comment: 0,0:22:27.64,0:22:30.16,ED - CN,,0,0,0,karaoke,相信我  请相信我
Comment: 0,0:22:30.83,0:22:33.33,ED - CN,,0,0,0,karaoke,你总会回到我的身边
Comment: 0,0:22:33.59,0:22:36.17,ED - CN,,0,0,0,karaoke,究竟是何种力量  维系着这份牵绊
Comment: 0,0:22:37.00,0:22:40.89,ED - CN,,0,0,0,karaoke,宛若地心引力
Comment: 0,0:22:41.83,0:22:46.95,ED - CN,,0,0,0,karaoke,即便我们归途各异
Comment: 0,0:22:47.84,0:22:51.64,ED - CN,,0,0,0,karaoke,你我之间的牵绊  也无从抗拒
Comment: 0,0:22:51.92,0:22:54.85,ED - CN,,0,0,0,karaoke,吸引着彼此 宛若地心引力
Comment: 0,0:22:55.36,0:23:00.23,ED - CN,,0,0,0,karaoke,怀抱彼岸的梦  方舟仍在流离
Comment: 0,0:23:00.68,0:23:05.37,ED - CN,,0,0,0,karaoke,且让我们相依  仰望天际  让这旅途延续
Comment: 0,0:23:06.30,0:23:11.37,ED - CN,,0,0,0,karaoke,即使你的心  只属于你自己
Comment: 0,0:23:11.76,0:23:13.16,ED - CN,,0,0,0,karaoke,我也想让你知晓
Comment: 0,0:23:13.16,0:23:17.20,ED - CN,,0,0,0,karaoke,在我的心底  永远存有你的容身之地
Comment: 0,0:23:17.54,0:23:20.61,ED - CN,,0,0,0,karaoke,究竟是何种力量  维系着这份牵绊
Comment: 0,0:23:20.88,0:23:23.96,ED - CN,,0,0,0,karaoke,宛若地心引力
Comment: 0,0:23:25.71,0:23:30.96,ED - CN,,0,0,0,karaoke,若你我注定殊途而归
Comment: 0,0:23:31.87,0:23:35.40,ED - CN,,0,0,0,karaoke,这挣不脱的牵绊啊
Comment: 0,0:23:35.71,0:23:38.71,ED - CN,,0,0,0,karaoke,令我为你倾心  如万物受引力坠向大地
